title: 12/28/21 DPS Hour 2   Rob Parker & TJ Houshmandzadeh Guest Hosting
itunes:title: 12/28/21 DPS Hour 2   Rob Parker & TJ Houshmandzadeh Guest Hosting
description:
Rob and TJ talk about the Dolphins' Monday Night win over the Saints. Rob is not buying into the Dolphins as a team that can make an impact in the post-season, TJ thinks there are a lot of good things going the Dolphins' way heading down the stretch. Rob and TJ break down the NFC Playoff picture, and narrow in on how the Cowboys and the Cardinals factor into things.
